  "title": "🌙 Night Shift Service Crew (Suntec City) | Up to $3,000 + Allowances!",
  "description": "<p>💰 <strong>Salary: $2,200 – $3,000 (Inclusive of Allowances)</strong><br />🚀 <strong>Immediate Hiring | No Experience Needed</strong></p><h2>🕒 <strong>Working Hours & Schedule</strong></h2><ul><li><strong>Night Shift:</strong> <em>5:00 PM – 2:00 AM</em> (or based on outlet schedule)</li><li><strong>Working Days:</strong> <em>6 days per week</em></li><li><strong>Rest Day:</strong> <em>1 weekday</em></li><li><strong>Weekends & PH required</strong></li></ul><h2>✨ <strong>Why Join Us?</strong></h2><ul><li>🚕 <strong>Transport Allowance</strong> up to <strong>$100</strong></li><li>🌙 <strong>Night Shift Allowance</strong> up to <strong>$150/night</strong></li><li>🍱 <strong>Staff Meals Provided</strong></li><li>👨‍👩‍👧 Friendly, supportive team environment</li><li>📈 Career progression in service & bar operations</li></ul><h2>🎯 <strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></h2><ol><li>Greet and seat customers warmly, ensuring a welcoming dining experience.</li><li>Take and serve orders accurately and promptly.</li><li>Provide detailed menu explanations (yakitori, beverages, specials).</li><li>Prepare and serve beverages, including alcoholic drinks.</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and restock bar/service area.</li><li>Assist with bar opening/closing duties.</li><li>Handle customer enquiries and feedback professionally.</li><li>Coordinate closely with kitchen staff for smooth operations.</li><li>Process payments and ensure accurate billing.</li><li>Uphold service quality, hygiene, and restaurant standards.</li><li>Work harmoniously with team members during peak hours.</li></ol><h2>👤 <strong>Who We’re Looking For</strong></h2><ul><li>Comfortable working late-night shifts</li><li>Positive, friendly, customer-focused attitude</li><li>Team player with good communication skills</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced environment</li><li>Experience is a bonus, but <strong>training provided</strong></li></ul><p>EA Personnel Name: Jabez Wong<br />EA Personnel No: R1762582<br />EA License No: 23C1703</p>",
